```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    package="com.alphabase389752.facebook-automation-script">
    
    <!-- 
        This is the AndroidManifest.xml for the Facebook automation script application. 
        This application is designed for automation on social media platforms like Facebook, 
        providing a user-friendly interface and 24/7 operations.
    -->

    <!-- Permissions required for the application -->
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
    <!-- 
        Permission to access the internet. 
        Necessary for connecting to social media platforms for automation tasks.
    -->

    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
    <!-- 
        Permission to write to external storage. 
        Used for saving logs and configuration files necessary for automation.
    -->

    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
    <!-- 
        Permission to read from external storage. 
        Required for accessing saved data and configuration files.
    -->

    <application
        android:allowBackup="true"
        android:icon="@mipmap/ic_launcher"
        android:label="Facebook automation script - Android Automation Tool"
        android:roundIcon="@mipmap/ic_launcher_round"
        android:supportsRtl="true"
        android:theme="@style/AppTheme">

        <!-- 
            Main Activity of the application.
            This is where the user will interact with the application.
        -->
        <activity android:name=".MainActivity">
            <intent-filter>
                <action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />

                <category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
            </intent-filter>
        </activity>

        <!-- 
            Automation Service for handling background tasks.
            This service will manage the automation processes for Facebook and other supported platforms.
        -->
        <service android:name=".AutomationService" 
                 android:enabled="true"
                 android:exported="false">
        </service>

    </application>

</manifest>
``` 

### 说明：
- `MainActivity` 是应用的主要入口，用户可以在此与Facebook自动化脚本进行交互。
- `AutomationService` 是用于处理自动化任务的后台服务，支持24小时不间断运行。
- 该应用可以在真实安卓手机、云手机或模拟器上运行，提供图形化界面，用户无需编写代码即可配置参数，极大提高了用户体验。
